  stickyNoteInfos:
  - title: 'Position Line:'
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 1484
      y: 640
      width: 262
      height: 180
    contents: 'A line is defined thanks to a line property.



      The line Sequencer
      is a 0-1 parameter that allows us to choose where on the line to spawn a particle.



      We
      use the spawnIndex. As we have two particles, their index will either be 0
      or 1. This means they will both be positioned on the extremity of the line.

'
    theme: 
    textSize: Small
    colorTheme: 2
  - title: 'Random Texindex:'
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 2447
      y: 1216
      width: 284
      height: 100
    contents: Setting a random value for texIndex attribute will offset each starting
      frame's animation
    theme: 
    textSize: Small
    colorTheme: 3
  - title: 'FlipBook Player:'
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 2447
      y: 1531
      width: 423
      height: 121
    contents: 'The Flipbook Player allows you to easily animate your flipbook or
      sprite sheet.

      Just give a frame rate and the block does the rest for
      you.

      In the background, this block is updating the texIndex value to
      animate the frame:

      texIndex +=  frameRate * delta Time ;

'
    theme: 
    textSize: Small
    colorTheme: 3
  - title: 'Noise:'
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 976
      y: 1799
      width: 258
      height: 148
    contents: "We're feeding the time into a 1D value noise to get some animated
      random values. Those values are used to give some life to our small flames
      by \u201Cnoising\u201D the angle and color attributes.\r\nThis gives some life
      by adding some random rotation movement and fake color illumination.\r\n"
    theme: 
    textSize: Small
    colorTheme: 2
  - title: 'UV Mode Flipbook Blend Frames:'
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 2841
      y: 2187
      width: 317
      height: 151
    contents: "The Flame on the Right has its UV move set to \u201Cflipbook blend\u201D.\r\nThis
      will blend or interpolate between frames and have smoother motion.\r\n"
    theme: 
    textSize: Small
    colorTheme: 3
  - title: 'UV Mode Flipbook :'
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 1449
      y: 2197
      width: 364
      height: 132
    contents: "The flame on the left has its UV move set to \u201Cflipbook,\u201D
      and the \u201Cflipbook blend frames\u201D option is turned off. This means
      that no blend or interpolation between frames is done during animation.\r\n\r\nDepending
      on your animation frame rate and the number of frames in your sprite sheet,
      this can cause animation stepping to be visible between each frame.\r\n"
    theme: 
    textSize: Small
    colorTheme: 3
  - title: FlipBook Flame
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 1975
      y: 31
      width: 605
      height: 101
    contents: 
    theme: 
    textSize: Huge
    colorTheme: 2
  categories: []
  uiBounds:
    serializedVersion: 2
    x: 921
    y: -29
    width: 2262
    height: 2659
